text: Tyrone A. Garner (born 1968/1969) is an American politician and retired police officer. He is the 30th mayor of Kansas City, Kansas since 2021. He was the deputy chief of the Kansas City Police Department. ==References== Category:1960s births Category:Living people Category:American mayors Category:American police officers Category:Politicians from Kansas Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:Politicians from San Jose, California Category:People from Kansas City, Kansas
